{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2ca6ae557e","title":"集中最大兵力歼灭当面之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"16476e6a6e","index":0,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":31,"articleId":"2ca6ae557e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"34f8254df6","type":"paragraph","text":"集中最大兵力歼灭当面之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"2ca6ae557e"},{"id":"45d1a50637","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年10月31日）刘、邓已令赵尔陆率六个主力团南下对付十六军，使你们安心歼灭当面之敌，望速指示赵部行进路线。你们是否还感兵力不足，除陈磨纵队主力外，一切在半月行程内可能调动之部队均可调动，以便集中最大兵力。杨张派赴邹腰地区协助陈黎作战之一个旅可即西调，四军已陆续入鲁，那边不需要了","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"2ca6ae557e"},{"id":"c8f0b54ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"2ca6ae557e"},{"id":"e223a84dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"西世[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋冀鲁豫军区司令员刘伯承和政治委员邓小平的电报。同一天，毛泽东还为中共中央军委起草了一份给赵尔陆的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"2ca6ae557e"}],"page":{"id":"cb88bc0b57","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"2ca6ae557e","start":497,"end":497}}}},"__N_SSG":true}